# Agent 5 — News Sentiment Intelligence Agent (Hedge Fund Level)

## Deep Analysis of [news.txt](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/news.txt) Blueprint

The blueprint defines a **7-step pipeline** that transforms raw financial news into structured market signals. Here is what was requested and what I am adding on top:

| Step | Blueprint Requirement | My Enhancement |
|------|----------------------|----------------|
| 1 | News Sources (GDELT, NewsAPI, CryptoPanic, RSS) | Add **deduplication**, **rate limiting**, **circuit breakers**, fallback chains |
| 2 | News Collector (feedparser) | Multi-source **async collector** with retry, caching, and health monitoring |
| 3 | News Cleaning (basic string ops) | Full **NLP pipeline**: dedup, language detection, boilerplate removal, relevance filtering |
| 4 | Embedding Model (MiniLM-L6-v2) | **Semantic similarity clustering** + duplicate detection via cosine similarity |
| 5 | Sentiment Analysis (FinBERT) | **Hybrid FinBERT + LLM** dual-analysis with confidence arbitration |
| 6 | Impact Score (basic formula) | **Multi-factor scoring**: source reputation × sentiment strength × topic importance × temporal recency × entity relevance |
| 7 | Entity Extraction (spaCy NER) | **Financial entity recognition** with custom asset ticker mapping + sector classification |
| — | Temporal Aggregation ("monster feature") | Full **momentum signals** (1h, 24h, 7d) with exponential weighted moving averages |
| — | Event Detection AI ("very important advice") | **Black swan detector**: Fed meetings, ETF approvals, regulation changes, geopolitical shocks |
| — | Integration with Agent 3 | Full pipeline integration with **schema contract**, orchestrator validation, and signal consumption |

