### Integration Layer

#### [MODIFY] [orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/orchestrator.py)

- Add Agent 5 to the pipeline **between Agent 1 and Agent 3**
- Agent 5 receives Agent 1 output as context (market regime awareness)
- Agent 5 output is validated against `Agent5Output` schema
- Agent 5 signals are passed to Agent 3 (allocation optimizer can bias weights based on news sentiment)
- Agent 5 signals are also passed to Agent 4 (risk supervisor evaluates news risk)

New pipeline flow:
```
Agent 1 (Macro) → Agent 5 (News) → Agent 2 (Profile) → Agent 3 (Strategist) → Agent 4 (Risk)
```

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/main.py)

- Add `--agent 5` / `--agent news` CLI entry
- Add `run_agent5()` function

